  "text": "Hello, and welcome to the Sao Paulo office. My name is Bruno. I work here on the third floor. We are a small team of six people. We work in the financial department. Every morning we have coffee together at nine o'clock. I am very glad to meet you, Anna. Welcome to the team.",
